{"tid":1553154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界文宣】一定要同啲鬼佬講警察帶頭搞破壞","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:32:18.000Z","uid":140738,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7655640213849183c85be01de1957e41b56e5734","tid":1553154,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"全連登都知警察扮示威者搞破壞，<br />\n<br />\n但好多黃絲但唔跟車咁貼嗰啲都唔知，<br />\n<br />\n文宣麻煩加強返依方面，<br />\n<br />\n話比啲人聽警察帶頭搞破壞，<br />\n<br />\n意頭搞散一個和平集會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要係同埋啲鬼佬講，<br />\n<br />\n啲鬼佬可能知五大訴求，<br />\n<br />\n知香港嘅情況，<br />\n<br />\n但佢地唔會想像到啲黑警會用啲咁低劣嘅手法，<br />\n<br />\n文宣嘅野唔可以停，<br />\n<br />\n特別今日活動同美國有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外 黑警扮示威者搞破壞已經係事實，<br />\n<br />\n咁記者報新聞嗰陣係咪應該用疑似示威者，<br />\n<br />\n或者用有示威者裝扮嘅人破壞，<br />\n<br />\n而唔係直接落結論話係示威者，<br />\n<br />\n依方面大家一齊研究下。"},{"pid":"550d2a21d832c4cf19d848bd02298329a461f2d3","tid":1553154,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"推比世界知"},{"pid":"587c5def66350dcdcffb8377d7b4dc140a72f493","tid":1553154,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b690592f8ad7e34512d2c5efb33951fa6345a721","tid":1553154,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"今日辛苦曬和理勇武手足<br />\n<br />\n鍵盤英文文宣開動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73adf565ae63db95df85116bdff6e1f91cfe6635","tid":1553154,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"文宣組"},{"pid":"96aeeb6d1fe2d86611142280b58d8ae540667b7a","tid":1553154,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"7e47500fb714451b4ae591694d2cea0af29a33c8","tid":1553154,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{